	h1 About &laquo;Fylik Project&raquo;
	p.
		Fylik Project is simple file sharing web application which allows you share your files with everyone easy, fastly and anonymously.

	h2 Why this project?
	p.
		Fylik Project was created as my test project for testing newest web frameworks. However, Fylik Project has features below:

