	h2 For coders
	p.
		Fylik Project is made as Progressive Web Application (PWA).
		<br><br>
		Client-side code was built with <b>Vue.JS</b>.
		<br><br>
		Fylik API was built with <b>Node.JS</b>, <b>Express.JS</b>, <b>MongoDB</b>.

